{"data":[{"date":"09:02 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Shkendija vs RB Salzburg 01h15 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhan-dinh-shkendija-vs-rb-salzburg-01h15-ngay-158-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Shkendija vs RB Salzburg l\u00fac 01h15 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Shkendija vs RB Salzburg 01h15 ng\u00e0y 158 c\u00fap C1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Shkendija vs RB Salzburg 01h15 ng\u00e0y 158 c\u00fap C1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Shkendija-vs-RB-Salzburg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Shkendija vs RB Salzburg</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Shkendija vs RB Salzburg: 1-3<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, Shkendija \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League. \u0110\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Macedonia ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh RB Salzburg. S\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 ngay tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i khi RB Salzburg d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, RB Salzburg \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra \u01b0u th\u1ebf qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thua v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00c1o v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00c1o c\u00f2n \u0111ang tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u0103ng hoa v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 11 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng (t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu). Trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 10 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG \u00c1o m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, RB Salzburg c\u0169ng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 3 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Marco Rose \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Shkendija ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00ean RB Salzburg th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o ra 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRB Salzburg \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng th\u0103ng hoa. 9/12 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00c1o k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Shkendija ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, RB Salzburg \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Shkendija v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ Shkendija (4-2-3-1): Zahov - Bejtulai, Adili, Musliu, Murati - Alimi, Totre - Selmani, Emini, Shefiti - Ibraimi.<br>\r\n+ RB Salzburg (4-3-1-2): Stankovic - Lainer, Pongracic, Ramalho, Ulmer - Schlager, Samassekou, Mwepu - Wolf\u00a0 - Yabo, Dabbur.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2353","checkdouble":"194440"},{"date":"09:53 14/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u Emery \u0111ang l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u1edbi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/huyen-thoai-khong-hieu-emery-dang-lam-gi-voi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tony Adams k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00ec nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd trong tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac trong th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda khi Arsenal nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i hai b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110KV\u0110 Man City ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, hai t\u00e2n binh Bernd Leno v\u00e0 Lucas Torreira b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u1ec9 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/huyen-thoai-khong-hieu-emery-dang-lam-gi-voi-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 c\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Tony Adams l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Emery: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Xhaka, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n Torreira, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecf con nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng minh, \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u00fang ta v\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh vai tr\u00f2 v\u1edbi N\u2019Golo Kante \u1edf Chelsea c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea1i sao Leno kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong khung th\u00e0nh c\u01a1 ch\u1ee9? T\u00f4i y\u00eau qu\u00fd Cech, m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng th\u00f4i n\u00e0o, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi r\u1ed3i. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1ea3 Maitland-Niles \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i n\u1eefa, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb non n\u1edbt kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Man City? Th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i t\u1edbi gi\u1edd v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u Emery \u0111ang l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u1edf Arsenal su\u1ed1t 5-6 tu\u1ea7n qua. N\u1ebfu l\u00e0 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m th\u00ec h\u1eb3n t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t n\u00f3ng m\u1eaft v\u1edbi anh ta l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2352","checkdouble":"194441"},{"date":"10:35 14/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen hay h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/chuyen-ve-naby-keita-phan-1-vua-cua-duong-pho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs U23 Nepal l\u00fac 19h ng\u00e0y 14/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs U23 Nepal 19h ng\u00e0y 148 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs U23 Nepal 19h ng\u00e0y 148 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/nhan-dinh-u23-nhat-ban-vs-u23-nepal-19h-ngay-14-8-vong-bang-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs U23 Nepal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs U23 Nepal: 4-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Cho d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 mang l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m HCV&nbsp;m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u1ee9 s\u1edf hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n, tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u khu v\u1ef1c \u1edf m\u1ecdi c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9. Trong danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 Asiad 2018, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ryosuke Kojima, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng d\u1ef1 FIFA&nbsp;U20 World Cup 2017 m\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a U20 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Asiad 2018 c\u1ee7a U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, khi ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 U23 Nepal - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trung b\u00ecnh y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c Nam \u00c1 v\u00e0 b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D m\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y t\u1eebn x\u1ebfp b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 (U23 Uzbekistan, U23 UAE v\u00e0 U23 Lebanon). Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb&nbsp; cho ASIAD 2018, U23 Nepal \u0111\u00e3 thua \u0111\u1eadm 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Th\u00e1i Lan - \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngang t\u1ea7m U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs U23 Nepal<br>\r\nU23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Ryosuke Kojima; Takahiro Yanagi, Teruki Hara, Honoya Shoji, Taiyo Koga; So Fujitani, Itsuki Urata, Koji Miyoshi, Tsukasa Morishima; Kyosuke Tagawa, Ren Komatsu.<br>\r\nU23 Nepal: Alan Neupane; Ananta Tamang, Kamal Shrestha, Budhathoki, Rajbanshi; Heman Gurung, Sunil Bal, Thapa Magar, Tej Tamang; Anjan Bista, Bimal Magar.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2351","checkdouble":"194443"},{"date":"09:17 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Fenerbahce vs Benfica 01h00 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhan-dinh-fenerbahce-vs-benfica-01h00-ngay-158-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fenerbahce vs Benfica l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Fenerbahce vs Benfica 01h00 ng\u00e0y 158 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Fenerbahce vs Benfica 01h00 ng\u00e0y 158 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Fenerbahce_vs_Benfica.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Fenerbahce vs Benfica</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Fenerbahce vs Benfica: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Fenerbahce tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 Champions League 2018/19 d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u00e1 qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, Fenerbahce \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c thay m\u00e1u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u00f3n t\u1edbi 7 t\u00e2n binh, trong \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Andre Ayew t\u1eeb CLB\u00a0Swansea t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1edd v\u1eady th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phillip Cocu \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 8/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. L\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 Champions League, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Benfica 0-1 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 g\u00ec qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i b\u1edfi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00ean nh\u1edb Fenerbahce s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng s\u00e2n b\u00e3i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. 20 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00f3n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Fenerbahce ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn (th\u1eafng 15). C\u00e1c SV\u0110 t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u1ed1n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng t\u1eeb l\u00e2u l\u00e0 ch\u1ea3o l\u1eeda kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i g\u00ec t\u1edbi Benfica.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Benfica thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Sukur Saracoglu c\u1ee7a Fenerbahce l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y 26/04/2013. Khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Benfica ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nFenerbahce: V.Demirel, M.\u0160krtel, M.Isla, R.Neust\u00e4dter, H.Kald\u0131r\u0131m, M.Valbuena, M.Topal, N.Dirar, Giuliano, A.Potuk, E.Elmas<br>\r\nBenfica: O.Vlachodimos, Andr\u00e9 Almeida, Jardel, \u00c1lex Grimaldo, R\u00faben Dias, L.Fejsa, Pizzi, E.Salvio, F.Cervi, Gedson Fernandes, F.Ferreyra</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2350","checkdouble":"194445"},{"date":"10:40 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhan-dinh-u23-trung-quoc-vs-u23-dong-timor-16h-ngay-148-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor l\u00fac 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor 16h ng\u00e0y 148 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor 16h ng\u00e0y 148 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/china.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor: 3-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 U23 \u0110\u00f4ng&nbsp;Timor c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7. C\u00f2n U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m HCV&nbsp;Asiad 2018. Trong 4 l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, tuy\u1ec3n U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 U23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor d\u1ef1 ASIAD. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 13 b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n, U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng song v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean 6-2.&nbsp;R\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Maddaloni c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Malaysia v\u00e0 U23 Iran (2-1 v\u00e0 3-2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb \u0110\u00f4ng Timor \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 m\u1ea5y n\u0103m qua. Nh\u01b0ng khi ra \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 canh tranh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i:<br>\r\nU23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c: Chen Wei; Li Hailong, Liu Yang, Gao Zhunyi, Deng Hanwen; Chen Zhechao, Yao Junsheng, Wei Shihao, Zhang Yuan; Feng Boyuan, Zhang Yuning.<br>\r\nU23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor: Ciro Gomez; Juliao Mendonca, Victor, Nelson, Gaspar Da Silva, Tomas Sarmento; Kasey Vergas, Jos\u00e9 Oliveira, Armindo De Almeida, Jos\u00e9 Fonseca, Rufino Gama.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2349","checkdouble":"194448"},{"date":"10:47 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs U23 Nepal 19h ng\u00e0y 14/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhan-dinh-u23-nhat-ban-vs-u23-nepal-19h-ngay-148-asiad