u1edf m\u00e0n Asiad 2018 c\u1ee7a U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, khi ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 U23 Nepal - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trung b\u00ecnh y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c Nam \u00c1 v\u00e0 b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D m\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y t\u1eebn x\u1ebfp b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 (U23 Uzbekistan, U23 UAE v\u00e0 U23 Lebanon). Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb&nbsp; cho ASIAD 2018, U23 Nepal \u0111\u00e3 thua \u0111\u1eadm 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Th\u00e1i Lan - \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngang t\u1ea7m U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs U23 Nepal<br>\r\nU23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Ryosuke Kojima; Takahiro Yanagi, Teruki Hara, Honoya Shoji, Taiyo Koga; So Fujitani, Itsuki Urata, Koji Miyoshi, Tsukasa Morishima; Kyosuke Tagawa, Ren Komatsu.<br>\r\nU23 Nepal: Alan Neupane; Ananta Tamang, Kamal Shrestha, Budhathoki, Rajbanshi; Heman Gurung, Sunil Bal, Thapa Magar, Tej Tamang; Anjan Bista, Bimal Magar.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2348","checkdouble":"194450"},{"date":"11:00 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Qatar 19h ng\u00e0y 14/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhan-dinh-u23-thai-lan-vs-u23-qatar-19h-ngay-148-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Qatar l\u00fac 19h ng\u00e0y 14/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Qatar 19h ng\u00e0y 148 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Qatar 19h ng\u00e0y 148 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/u23-thai-lan-vs-u23-qatar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Qatar</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Qatar: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U23 Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i d\u00f9 theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh, m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng Worrawoot v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn l\u1ec7nh t\u1eeb L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. N\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng 20 tri\u1ec7u bath (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 14 t\u1ef7 VN\u0110).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Nepal 4-0. HLV Worrawoot r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u00d4ng cho hay:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u01a1i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Uzbekistan, Qatar v\u00e0 Bangladesh, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua U23 Qatar \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd\". <br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 U23 Th\u00e1i Lan, U23 Qatar c\u0169ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0o. Trong \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf CLB Eupen thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i\u00a0V\u0110QG B\u1ec9. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, ng\u00f4i sao Mohammed t\u1eeb CLB h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Leeds United c\u0169ng quay v\u1ec1 chung l\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1eadt c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U23 Qatar \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm ra sao. Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2347","checkdouble":"194451"},{"date":"11:11 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Middlesbrough vs Notts County 01h45 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhan-dinh-middlesbrough-vs-notts-county-01h45-ngay-158-cup-lien-doan-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Middlesbrough vs Notts County l\u00fac 01h45 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Anh League Cup 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Middlesbrough vs Notts County 1h45 ng\u00e0y 158 League Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Middlesbrough vs Notts County 1h45 ng\u00e0y 158 League Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Middlesbrough-vs-Notts-County.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Middlesbrough vs Notts County</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Middlesbrough vs Notts County: 2-2 (Boro th\u1eafng hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 ho\u1eb7c lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</strong>M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Middlesbrough \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 5 chung cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh, v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong v\u00f2ng playoff gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Premier League. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tony Pulis ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, 1 h\u00f2a sau 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean BXH.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Notts County \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eed th\u00e1ch qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Boro. Notts County \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf League Two (h\u1ea1ng 4), t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 k\u00e9m Boro t\u1edbi 2 h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea5u. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, Notts County c\u00f2n \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua chu\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf League Two, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi to\u00e0n thua \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, nh\u1eefng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea5y Middlesbrough kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7n nh\u1edb Boro t\u1eebng g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Notts County ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Riverside t\u1ea1i C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 12 n\u0103m.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br />\r\n* 3 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Middlesbrough th\u1eafng 2, Notts County th\u1eafng 1<br />\r\n* 2 l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Notts County tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Middlesbrough th\u1eafng 1, thua 1<br />\r\n* L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t 2 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Anh m\u00f9a 2006/07, khi \u0111\u00f3 Notts County \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Middlesbrough.<br />\r\n* 2 trong s\u1ed1 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Middlesbrough t\u1ea1i C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Anh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng 3 Anh (Notts County n\u0103m 2006 v\u00e0 Accrington Stanley n\u0103m 2013)<br />\r\n* HLV Tony Pulis \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Notts County t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 11/1999 \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 4-4 d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV c\u1ee7a Bristol City.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br />\r\nMiddlesbrough: Jordan Hugill ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ra s\u00e2n; Daniel Ayala v\u00e0 Rudy Gestede s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br />\r\nNotts County: Christian Oxlade-Chamberlain v\u00e0 Ben Hall s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2346","checkdouble":"194452"},{"date":"11:47 14/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/link-xem-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-pakistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Pakistan v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 14/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng cao nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd v\u1eeba b\u01b0\u1edbc ra t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nH\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine, Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan c\u00e0ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Pakistan link xem Asiad 2018 HD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Pakistan link xem Asiad 2018 HD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/vietnam-pakistan-2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Pakistan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 1 trong hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D.\u00a0 D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c k\u1ef7 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Indonesia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu tinh th\u1ea7n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, trong 3 ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t Indonesia, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u00e2n c\u1ecf nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, do s\u00e2n c\u1ecf m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ee7a Samsung t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Java ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u2018t\u1eadp chay\u2019 tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t xi m\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (14/8).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u an \u1ee7i l\u00e0 trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o nhau gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0 l\u00f2ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a NHM.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ASIAD, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m \u2018thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi kinh nghi\u1ec7m\u2019. Ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. R\u1ea5t may \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang seo c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o may m\u1eafn.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2345","checkdouble":"194453"},{"date":"11:55 14/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan: Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 t\u00edch m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ky-tich-moi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn cho r\u1eb1ng k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n hai. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ee9ng minh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 may m\u1eafn.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/link-xem-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-pakistan-372-194453.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/link-xem-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/link-xem-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-pakistan-372-194453.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1eeb k\u1ef3 t\u00edch U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, khi m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u1edf c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Australia v\u00e0 Syria.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Miura \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 3 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Jordan, UAE v\u00e0 \u00dac, qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Miura b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sa th\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn xa h\u01a1n, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng \u00edt gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u00f9ng c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111i t\u1eeb h\u1ebft b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0y sang b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u01afCV v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 t\u00edch m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 t\u00edch m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/30/Xem-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Pakistan-Khoi-dau-ky-tich-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 t\u00edch v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u1eafng h\u1eadu \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 t\u00edch v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u1eafng h\u1eadu trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi ch\u00fang ta t\u1eeb t\u00e2m th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng &lsquo;l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 t\u00edch l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u n\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ea7n hai v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo, khi m\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u00ecn h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng &lsquo;l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng&rsquo;. Khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch c\u1eb7n k\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD n\u0103m nay gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng hay Toshiya Miura \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf hai k\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111i xa t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111ang c\u1ea7n l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i b\u1edfi m\u1ecdi t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia v\u00e0 Bahrain. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/olympic-vietnam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 b\u1edfi U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Do \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebfn. V\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c hay kh\u00f4ng v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u00f2n l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng g\u1eb7p Pakistan v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 14/8. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i s\u1ebd c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec, v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c, th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Khi th\u1ea7y Park t\u1ef1 tin<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y xu\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin cho bi\u1ebft: : &ldquo;\u0110\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra khi V-League v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac, n\u00ean t\u00f4i tin l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u1edf m\u1ee9c cao. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua c\u0169ng gi\u00fap to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD 2018&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam Park Hang Seo\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/binhluan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 trang b\u1ecb cho&nbsp;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 tin \u1edf ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1 v\u00e0 Trung \u00c1. To\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang 2 l\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Quang H\u1ea3i, Duy M\u1ea1nh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng,&hellip; th\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a 3 &lsquo;l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng&rsquo; Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, s\u1eafc b\u00e9n trong d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. H\u01a1n h\u1ebft, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. &lsquo;S\u00fang \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean n\u00f2ng&rsquo;, v\u00e0 h\u00e3y ch\u1edd xem m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau-168-194432.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau-168-194432.html\">Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi VTV kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8): Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch</span><br>\r\nNHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2344","checkdouble":"194454"},{"date":"07:41 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8): Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>NHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan.</h2><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; Khi kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng cao nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd v\u1eeba b\u01b0\u1edbc ra t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine, Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan c\u00e0ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 1 trong hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p>D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c k\u1ef7 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 148) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 148) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Indonesia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu tinh th\u1ea7n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, trong 3 ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t Indonesia, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u00e2n c\u1ecf nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, do s\u00e2n c\u1ecf m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ee7a Samsung t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Java ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 &lsquo;t\u1eadp chay&rsquo; tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t xi m\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (14/8).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u an \u1ee7i l\u00e0 trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o nhau gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0 l\u00f2ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a NHM.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ASIAD, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m &lsquo;thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi kinh nghi\u1ec7m&rsquo;. Ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. R\u1ea5t may \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang seo c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o may m\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 &lsquo;\u1ea9n s\u1ed1&rsquo; Olympic Pakistan<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pakistan c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi su\u1ed1t 3 n\u0103m qua, h\u1ecd b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sau \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb L\u0110B\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi FIFA.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 n\u0103m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pakistan &lsquo;\u00e2m th\u1ea7m luy\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng&rsquo; \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ASIAD 2018 - gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea5p ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u00c1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khan hi\u1ebfm th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y song r\u1ea5t may m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9n b\u0103ng ghi h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Pakistan t\u1ea1i Bahrain m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n th\u00f4ng tin qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eafm r\u00f5 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ban \u0111\u1ea7u, Pakistan kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n hung tin khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kaleemullah Khan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i xin h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n mu\u1ed9n v\u00ec v\u01b0\u1edbng b\u1eadn th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 Pakistan t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f4ng coi tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0u c\u1edd s\u1eafc \u00e1o.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Olympic Pakistan\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Pakistan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Cac-doi-thu-tai-ASIAD-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-manh-yeu-the-nao-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Pakistan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Olympic Pakistan c\u00f3 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 20 tu\u1ed5i. Ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Saddam Hussain. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hussain hi\u1ec7n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Larnaka Gencler Birligi S.K, CLB c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea3o S\u00edp. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i (c\u00f9ng Yousuf Butt) trong l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Pakistan. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 19 tr\u1eadn cho \u0110T Pakistan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung, \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Pakistan ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1ee9 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 khi\u00eam nh\u01b0\u1eddng. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00eam ASIAD v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1 th\u1eafng, 2 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 1 thua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. Trong cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 - 4 - 3. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n&nbsp;\u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng, ch\u00fang ta ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Palestien hay Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf&nbsp;gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.T\u1ef1 tin nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng s\u01a1 h\u1edf, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:&#xA;115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan: 2-0<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:&nbsp;</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>+ Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu; \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft; Quang H\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>+ Olympic Pakistan: Saqib Hanif; Mohsin Ali, Umar Hayat, Mohammad Sohail, Muhammad Bilal; Khan Niazi, Saddam Hussain, Basit Amin, Mehmood Khan; Mohammad Riaz, Maqbool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-khi-thay-park-da-lo-het-168-194191.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-khi-thay-park-da-lo-het.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-khi-thay-park-da-lo-het-168-194191.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD: Khi th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u00e3 lo h\u1ebft</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa. V\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y NHM c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, khi m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 lo...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2343","checkdouble":"194428"},{"date":"07:38 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dynamo Kiev vs Slavia Praha 23h30 ng\u00e0y 14/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhan-dinh-dynamo-kiev-vs-slavia-praha-23h30-ngay-148-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dynamo Kiev vs Slavia Praha l\u00fac 23h30 ng\u00e0y 14/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dynamo Kiev vs Slavia Praha 23h30 ng\u00e0y 148 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dynamo Kiev vs Slavia Praha 23h30 ng\u00e0y 148 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Dynamo-Kiev-vs-Slavia-Praha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dynamo Kiev vs Slavia Praha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Dynamo Kiev vs Slavia Praha: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, do ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch n\u00ean Dynamo Kiev ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat s\u01a1 h\u1edf \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ukraine b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0o ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Tuy v\u1eady, v\u1edbi v\u1ed1n li\u1ebfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, Dynamo Kiev chi\u1ebfm ch\u00fat \u01b0u th\u1ebf trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n b\u00e3i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. 6 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 4 l\u1ea7n theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Ukraine lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh bi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi: g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ngc\u00f2n khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu, Dynamo Kiev ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Slavia Praha \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi 7 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (6 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng). Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u00ean, Dynamo Kiev khi g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00ec h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, \u01b0u ti\u00ean ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Slavia Praha c\u0169ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u1eeba qua. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Kiev c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1eed th\u00e1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng playoff song s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2342","checkdouble":"194429"},{"date":"07:51 14/08","title":"Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u201cb\u00e1o th\u00f9\u201d Barca th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ngc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/6/roma-chuan-bi-bao-thu-barca-thanh-cong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David Seaman th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng ra m\u1eb7t khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Manchester City.\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1ed7i hi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva nh\u1ea5m ch\u00ecm Emirates v\u00e0 x\u00f3a nh\u00f2a m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19 cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t Arsenal d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec3n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c so v\u1edbi th\u1eddi Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 Arsene Wenger.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal vs Man City M\u00e8o v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n m\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal vs Man City M\u00e8o v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n m\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/huyen-thoai-ngan-ngam-arsenal-meo-van-hoan-meo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal vs Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i David Seaman c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 55 tu\u1ed5i: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t Arsenal x\u01b0a c\u0169 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Ainsley Maitland-Niles khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ai h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb Kyle Walker r\u1ed3i Riyad Mahrez thi nhau h\u00e0nh cho ra b\u00e3. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh l\u1ea1i d\u00e2ng l\u00ean qu\u00e1 cao m\u00e0 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. C\u00e1ch ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Emery r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5y.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0nh \u00edt d\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn derby London. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Maurizio Sarri tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2341","checkdouble":"194430"},{"date":"07:52 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dinamo Zagreb vs Astana 01h00 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhan-dinh-dinamo-zagreb-vs-astana-01h00-ngay-158-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dinamo Zagreb vs Astana l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dinamo Zagreb vs Astana 1h00 ng\u00e0y 158 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dinamo Zagreb vs Astana 1h00 ng\u00e0y 158 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Dinamo-Zagreb-vs-Astana.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dinamo Zagreb vs Astana</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Dinamo Zagreb vs Astana: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Kazakhstan, Dinamo Zagreb b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi. Tuy v\u1eady, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Croatia \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i \u01b0u th\u1ebf l\u1edbn cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nenad Bjelica b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed thua v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u, Dinamo Zagreb v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng playoff.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 l\u00fd, Dinamo Zagreb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng song gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Croatia. Ngo\u00e0i \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n b\u00e3i, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Dinamo Zagreb lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2, khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Hapoel Beer Sheva (Israel), Dinamo Zagreb \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 5-0. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Astana, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eadp ra k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Kazakhstan \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng song tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Astana \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam nay, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 t\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u1ee9c kh\u00e1 cao. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng 5/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Dinamo Zagreb k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Dinamo Zagreb \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Astana.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ Dinamo Zagreb (4-2-3-1): Zagorac - Stojanovic, Theophile-Catherine, Dilaver, Leovac - Gojak, Sunjic - Hajrovic, Orsic, Olmo - Budimir.<br>\r\n+ Astana (4-1-4-1): Eric - Rukavina, Postnikov, Anicic, Shomko - Maevskiy - Tomasov, Kleinheisler, Muzhikov, Henrique - Kabananga</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2340","checkdouble":"194431"},{"date":"07:57 14/08","title":"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi VTV kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, do m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed ch\u00e0o b\u00e1n b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u2018b\u00e1n l\u1ebb\u2019 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00ean \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam VTV \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c NHM ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo th\u00f4ng qua internet. Song NHM s\u1ebd xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Xem-truc-tiep-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Pakistan-o-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>NHM c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan tr\u00ean trang vidio.com.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00f4ng qua website vidio.com.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 website ph\u00e1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ASIAD 2018 \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem vidio.com l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c k\u00ec ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Website n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfu tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam trong c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb 10/8 \u0111\u1ebfn 12/8 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, website vidio.com d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Pakistan./.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:\n10.0pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8): Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch</span><br>\r\nNHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2339","checkdouble":"194432"}]}